item.paragraph:
Pregnancy: Based on animal data, may cause fetal harm. (




                                       8.1

                                 )

text.paragraph:
Although the data from the clinical trials support use of Pantoprazole for the short-term treatment of EE associated with GERD in pediatric patients 1 year through 5 years, there is no commercially available dosage formulation appropriate for patients less than 5 years of age [


  see Dosage and Administration (



                                       2
                                    )


  ].
